---
---

<section class="architect">
  <div class="container architect-grid">
    <div class="architect-text">
      <span class="architect-badge reveal" style="--reveal-rot: -6deg; --reveal-rot-end: -2deg;">The Architect</span>
      <h2 class="architect-heading reveal">
        Laying Out The<br />Future Of Fluency
      </h2>

      <p class="architect-bio reveal">
        Language Layouts was born from a simple observation: most language learners fail not
        because they lack ability, but because they lack a system.
      </p>
      <p class="architect-bio reveal">
        As a teacher and language learner, I've spent years refining the intersection of Paul Nation's
        research and the science of learning.
      </p>
      <p class="architect-bio reveal">
        These layouts take that research and make it practical, giving teachers and learners a balanced
        approach to language that actually works.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="architect-photo reveal" style="--reveal-rot: 7deg; --reveal-rot-end: 3deg;">
      <div class="photo-card">
        <span class="tape photo-tape"></span>
        <img src="/images/architect-photo.jpeg" alt="Language Layouts architect" loading="lazy" />
        <span class="photo-caption hand-note">the human behind the layouts</span>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-accent" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 80 30" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M5 15 C15 10, 25 20, 35 15 C45 10, 55 20, 65 15 C70 12, 75 15, 80 13" stroke="var(--terra)" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .architect {
    padding-top: 60px;
  }

  .architect-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .architect-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    width: fit-content;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terra);
    border: 2px solid var(--terra);
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .architect-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .architect-bio {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .architect-photo {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* Polaroid-style frame */
  .photo-card {
    position: relative;
    width: 340px;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 2px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    padding: 14px 14px 12px;
    transition: transform 0.5s var(--ease-spring), box-shadow 0.5s var(--ease-out);
  }

  .architect-photo.visible .photo-card:hover {
    transform: rotate(-2deg) translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lift);
  }

  .photo-card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 360px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .photo-tape {
    top: -14px;
    left: 50%;
    margin-left: -46px;
    transform: rotate(4deg);
  }

  .photo-caption {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 10px;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .photo-accent {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -14px;
    right: -18px;
    width: 100px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .architect-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .photo-card {
      width: 280px;
    }

    .photo-card img {
      height: 300px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .photo-card {
      max-width: 80vw;
    }
  }
</style>
